# Implementation Plan — Phase 7: Calibration to NEXUS Standard

This phase focuses on calibrating the IdeaForge CLI to produce high-density artifacts (PRDs, System Designs, etc.) that meet the NEXUS v1.0 standard.

## Proposed Changes

### [Models]
Update `ollama_provider.py` to increase `num_predict` values, allowing for longer generations required by the new templates.

